If C (a masked individual is crawling out) and D (the bag is full of jewelry), then it strongly suggests criminal intent.
(ğ¶âˆ§ğ·)â‡’criminalÂ activity
If both suspicious and criminal activity are observed, then the masked individual is likely dishonest (E).

